<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>标题：</strong>NECO’S キッチン　～SCP財団ロゴのステーキ～<br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jiraku-mogana" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4062604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4062604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571120" alt="Jiraku_Mogana" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4062604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jiraku-mogana" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4062604); return false;">Jiraku_Mogana</a></span><br />
<strong>翻译：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3699277&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571120" alt="BenjaminChong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3699277)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/benjaminchong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3699277); return false;">BenjaminChong</a></span><br />
<strong>发布年份：</strong>2019</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>各位观众早上好。<br />
我是主持人[已编辑]博士，今天让我们一起愉快的料理吧！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>大家晚上好！我是助手[已编辑]。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><span style="font-size:0%;">在下是猫大厨请多关照</span></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>[已编辑]助手，今天我们要来做一道大菜。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>真的吗，博士。我现在的心情就好像上次用<a href="/scp-056-jp">SCP-056-JP</a>时一样激动！今天我们要做什么菜色呢？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>今天这道大菜要用到一些适合来做大菜的大菜材料。走，我们去收集食材吧！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>现在就去？这可真让我惊讶。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>出发吧！门口有我准备好的<a href="/scp-1365">BIKE JUSTICE</a>。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<hr />
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>我们到了。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>我们现在在深山老林里！究竟是要去采什么食材呢？平菇？栗茸？还是毒蝇伞？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>并不是。怎么就想着去采蘑菇了？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>那究竟是────</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>嘘！安静。它就在附近，可不能把它吓跑了。你看那边。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>嗯？什么东西在那边？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF/medium.jpg" width="300px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4/medium.jpg" width="300px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>啊！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E8%B2%A1%E5%9B%A3%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B4%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF/medium.jpg" width="300px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>是基金会标志<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup>～～～～！！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E7%AC%91%E9%A1%94/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>好家伙，这么大只，可是捡到宝了。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>我还是头一次看见野生的基金会标志呢。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>毕竟它们因为最近的<a href="/scp-4065">基金会标志排斥运动</a>数量减了不少。这几年的小孩子们甚至都以为基金会标志只生活在左上角呢。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>博士，赶紧把它抓起来吧！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>[已编辑]助手，你知道基金会标志的特殊捕获措施(Special Capture Procedures)吗？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>呃……拿这把<a href="/scp-572">SCP-572</a>给斩立决了？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>你从哪掏出来的，放回去，不是它。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>不，可用这把剑肯定能一刀两断呀！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>我们这次是要活捉的，劈成两半可不好。这剑我就没收了。<br />
基金会标志需要用诱饵引上钩的。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%94%B6%E5%AE%B9%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4.png" style="width:200px;" alt="控制收容保护.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:200px;">
<p>基金会标志的诱饵。</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>来，我们设一个陷阱。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E7%BD%A01/medium.jpg" width="300px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E7%BD%A02/medium.jpg" width="300px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E6%8D%95%E7%8D%B2/medium.jpg" width="300px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>我们抓到它了，博士！<br />
……嗯？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E9%96%89%E3%81%98%E3%82%8B%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B4/medium.jpg" width="200px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>箭头凑到一块了！<br />
博士，这是怎么回事？！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>唔，这是……</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E9%96%8B%E3%81%8F%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B4/medium.jpg" width="200px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E3%81%8F%E3%81%97%E3%82%83%E3%81%BF%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B4/medium.jpg" width="200px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>呃，似乎只是打了个喷嚏而已。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>啊，标志原来还会打喷嚏的吗？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<hr />
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>于是我们回到了厨房。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>终于要开始做菜了吗？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>我们先处理一下基金会标志吧。<br />
首先，把箭头拆下来。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E4%B8%8B%E5%87%A6%E7%90%861/medium.jpg" width="200px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>本体的突起部分有苦味，所以要把它切掉。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E4%B8%8B%E5%87%A6%E7%90%862/medium.jpg" width="200px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>用<a href="/scp-3794">SCP-3794</a>将本体部分敲软后，在一面上撒上盐、胡椒和██████████。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>把橄榄油倒进平底锅中，并加入蒜片炒香，然后用大火煎基金会标志。请注意，撒过盐的那一面需要向下。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E8%AA%BF%E7%90%86/medium.jpg" width="200px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>往朝上的一面也撒上盐、胡椒和██████████，在另一面煎好后翻面。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>金黄金黄的，看上去好好吃啊！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E7%AC%91%E9%A1%94/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>再煎上30秒，然后包进铝箔中，用平底锅的余温热至全熟。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>在这期间，我们来做酱料吧。请把刚刚拆下的箭头切成不影响口感的大小。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>这样可以吗？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%88%BB%E3%81%BF%E7%9F%A2%E5%8D%B0/medium.jpg" width="200px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>很好！然后往里加入<a href="/scp-2484">沙拉酱</a>、醋拌匀，塔塔酱就做好了。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>最后，把它们码在盘子里，大菜就完成了！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:400px;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90/medium.jpg" style="width:400px;" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:400px;">
<p>香煎基金会标志<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-2')">2</a></sup></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>那么[已编辑]助手，请试吃一下吧。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>哎，这个好吃！口感香滑，肉汁满溢，太棒了！<br />
果然新鲜的基金会标志就是不一样啊！我不由得<a href="/scp-2317">像巨人一样</a>把它吃光光了。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p><a href="/scp-2317">巨人</a>……？<br />
酱料你感觉如何？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>箭头香脆爽口，沙拉酱也很配本体的莎莎酱风味。3<a href="/old:scp-1548">星</a>好评！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E3%82%B0%E3%83%83%E3%83%89" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>3个<a href="/old:scp-1548">星</a>……！？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A1" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div class="joshu">
<div class="joshuword">
<p>哎呀，好吃到飞起啊。我现在感觉我好像看到了一片花田……</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E7%AC%91%E9%A1%94/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div class="hakase">
<div class="hakaseword">
<p>[已编辑]助手，不知道为什么，周围真的出现了一片花田。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/necos-kitchen/%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E6%82%A9%E3%82%80/medium.jpg" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 20px;" width="120px" alt="medium.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
